00:58:53,900 --> 00:58:55,340
 i nakon toga se to više nije dešavalo,

636
00:58:56,160 --> 00:58:56,760
 i onda opet,

637
00:58:56,760 --> 00:58:59,700
 razmišljam i sebe stavljam u taj kontekst,

638
00:58:59,700 --> 00:59:01,380
 pa njemu je teško,

639
00:59:01,380 --> 00:59:02,080
 nije meni teško,

640
00:59:02,080 --> 00:59:03,860
 šta me ne može biti teško,

641
00:59:03,860 --> 00:59:06,200
 šta je danas da trčim dva sata ili nešto,

642
00:59:06,200 --> 00:59:06,820
 šta mi je teško,

643
00:59:06,820 --> 00:59:07,960
 ne kužim, šta mi je teško,

644
00:59:07,960 --> 00:59:08,580
 sve su auto,

645
00:59:08,580 --> 00:59:09,700
 puno vozim,

646
00:59:09,700 --> 00:59:11,000
 puno sam u autu,

647
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:11,640
 i poslam,

648
00:59:11,640 --> 00:59:12,840
 i s tim tog si jedno nekad,

649
00:59:12,840 --> 00:59:13,400
 ne znam,

650
00:59:13,400 --> 00:59:14,180
 bojim u tome,

651
00:59:14,180 --> 00:59:15,840
 tog prometa,

652
00:59:15,840 --> 00:59:16,460
 tog ovoga,

653
00:59:16,460 --> 00:59:18,380
 ali,

654
00:59:18,380 --> 00:59:20,120
 niš mi je teško,

655
00:59:20,120 --> 00:59:21,920
 ja dan danas imam energiju,

656
00:59:21,920 --> 00:59:22,820
 i želim da tu,

657
00:59:23,160 --> 00:59:26,880
 znači najveći uspjeh moj bi bio da tu energiju naslijede moja djeca,

658
00:59:26,880 --> 00:59:29,760
 to bi bio moj uspjeh onako,

659
00:59:29,760 --> 00:59:31,100
 ovo sve ostalo,

660
00:59:31,100 --> 00:59:34,860
 želio bi da oni osjete strastu uspjeha,

661
00:59:34,860 --> 00:59:36,600
 ne novca,

662
00:59:36,600 --> 00:59:37,200
 ne ovoga,

663
00:59:37,200 --> 00:59:38,000
 nova će doći,

664
00:59:38,000 --> 00:59:39,040
 nova će proći,

665
00:59:39,040 --> 00:59:39,740
