01:00:27,520 --> 01:00:28,700
 e, ima nas drugačih,

692
01:00:28,700 --> 01:00:30,920
 ima nas drugačih koji gradimo nešto,

693
01:00:30,920 --> 01:00:32,940
 koji nešto napravimo i koji želim da to budemo,

694
01:00:32,940 --> 01:00:34,300
 možda nekome,

695
01:00:34,300 --> 01:00:35,980
 ne mislim primjera,

696
01:00:35,980 --> 01:00:37,640
 ali nekome da neko može,

697
01:00:37,760 --> 01:00:41,060
 ali mi smo iz nule potekli i došli smo do nečego,

698
01:00:41,060 --> 01:00:41,600
 svorili smo,

699
01:00:41,600 --> 01:00:43,700
 znači nismo imali priču,

700
01:00:43,700 --> 01:00:50,580
 to je onaj svijest da se moraš pripremiti da će nekada to doće,

701
01:00:50,580 --> 01:00:51,220
 doće loše,

702
01:00:51,220 --> 01:00:51,860
 doće i dobro,

703
01:00:51,860 --> 01:00:54,560
 isto tako je jako bitno prepoznati dobro i loše,

704
01:00:55,760 --> 01:00:56,580
