777
01:02:47,520 --> 01:02:48,820
 sami smo morali sve napraviti.

778
01:02:49,580 --> 01:02:50,420
 I to smo izgurali.

779
01:02:50,420 --> 01:02:51,480
 Ja sam rekao ljudima,

780
01:02:51,480 --> 01:02:52,360
 od ovoga,

781
01:02:52,360 --> 01:02:54,460
 vjerojatno ćemo ostati invalidije,

782
01:02:54,460 --> 01:02:55,380
 ostati ćemo bez jedna ruke,

783
01:02:55,380 --> 01:02:55,980
 ali idemo dalje.

784
01:02:55,980 --> 01:02:57,580
 Idemo dalje,

785
01:02:57,580 --> 01:02:58,400
 mi moramo išta dalje.

786
01:02:58,400 --> 01:03:00,300
 I to nam se polako vratilo,

787
01:03:00,300 --> 01:03:03,260
