01:05:43,160 --> 01:05:43,880
 rekao sam ja,

867
01:05:43,880 --> 01:05:45,080
 kad smo imali,

868
01:05:45,080 --> 01:05:46,040
 kad smo počinjali,

869
01:05:46,040 --> 01:05:48,040
