870
01:05:48,040 --> 01:05:48,360
 imamo,

871
01:05:49,260 --> 01:05:50,320
 ja ležim na onoj kopijki,

872
01:05:50,320 --> 01:05:51,200
 tamo na ovom pjesku,

873
01:05:51,200 --> 01:05:53,520
